			src="https://castrguru-assets.netlify.app/rose/avatar.webp"
			alt="Rose avatar"
			class="size-48 border-2 border-fuchsia-600 rounded-full shadow"
		/>

		<h1 class="text-6xl text-center text-fuchsia-800 tracking-wide">
			Ros√© Frame Kit
		</h1>

		<h1 class="text-4xl text-center text-fuchsia-600 tracking-tight">
			by Castr G√úR≈≤
		</h1>

		<h3 class="p-5 sm:p-10 text-2xl text-pretty text-center">
			To get going, open the <code class="text-sky-500 font-semibold">src/pages</code>
			directory in your project and start editing.
		</h3>
	</section>

	<div class="mx-10 border-t border-fuchsia-400" />

	<section class="my-10 flex flex-col gap-6">
		<h1 class="text-4xl font-medium text-slate-700 tracking-wider">
			üë∑‚Äç‚ôÇÔ∏è Hey, Builder!
