		<p class="text-lg/8 text-slate-700">
			This template comes with a few integrations already configured in your <code class="p-1 bg-slate-200">astro.config.mjs</code> file.
			You can customize your setup with <a href="https://astro.build/integrations" class="text-sky-500 font-medium text-xl hover:underline">Astro Integrations</a> to add tools like Tailwind, React, or Vue to your project.
