		<h4 class="text-xl/8 font-medium text-slate-700">
			Here are a few ideas on how to get started:
		</h4>

		<ul class="pl-10 list-disc text-lg/9 text-slate-700">
			<li>Edit this page in <code class="p-1 bg-slate-200">src/pages/index.astro</code></li>
			<li>Edit the site header items in <code class="p-1 bg-slate-200">src/components/Header.astro</code></li>
			<li>Add your name to the footer in <code class="p-1 bg-slate-200">src/components/Footer.astro</code></li>
			<li>Check out the included blog posts in <code class="p-1 bg-slate-200">src/content/blog/</code></li>
			<li>Customize the blog post page layout in <code class="p-1 bg-slate-200">src/layouts/BlogPost.astro</code></li>
		</ul>

		<p class="text-lg/8 text-slate-700">
			<strong>Have fun!</strong>
			If you get stuck, remember to <a href="https://docs.astro.build/" class="text-sky-500 font-medium text-xl hover:underline">read the Astro docs</a>
			or <a href="https://astro.build/chat" class="text-sky-500 font-medium text-xl hover:underline">join the Astro Discord</a> to ask questions.
		</p>

		<p class="text-lg/8 text-slate-700">
			If you're looking for a template well-suited for a 1st-time builder <em>(w/ little to no coding experience)</em>,
			then check out <a href="/kit/my-1st-frame" class="text-xl font-bold text-sky-500 hover:underline">My 1st Frame</a> kit.
		</p>
	</section>
